dct_title_s: Map of Sikkim and parts of the adjacent territories [cartographic material] : to illustrate sir R. Temple's paper / [lithographed by] W. & A. K. Johnston, Edinburgh & London. (geotiff)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Boundaries of Sikkim with Nepal, Tibet, Bhutan, Chumbi Valley, and Bengal Province are shown. Roads and mountain passes are shown. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 3 (1881), no. 6, pp. 321-40; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
